    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into what feels like a brand-new vehicle! This car is in absolute mint condition, having been meticulously maintained to showroom standards. Every detail is pristine, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior, offering a truly premium driving experience for its next owner. It\u2019s a rare find that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line!",
