    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. Mechanically, the engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly without any hesitation. The interior is clean and free of major wear, though you may find some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior consistent with careful use. All electronics and features are fully functional, ensuring a comfortable and worry-free driving experience.",
