      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several minor dings, some paint fading on the hood, and light surface scratches consistent with regular driving. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, functional choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard and offered in truly mint condition. Every detail reflects a commitment to preservation, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality specimen that performs with the precision of a new machine. Meticulously inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
