    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly collector-grade specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes; it has been professionally ceramic coated to maintain this showroom shine. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new\u2014the premium leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the dashboard remains untouched by UV exposure, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest interior light, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road debris. This car represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that drives, looks, and feels exactly as it did the day it was delivered from the factory.",
